       wanting to see me?

06:37.431 --> 06:41.533
  You know, taking a genuine
  interest, asking them things,

06:41.535 --> 06:43.535
   wondering what they think,
   maybe listening to them?

06:43.537 --> 06:45.871
     I'm running New York's
     top model agency,

06:45.873 --> 06:47.906
      one that will launch
      you into a career

