    that will take care
    of you your entire life.

06:51.545 --> 06:54.513
   Darling, I cannot give you
   my attention all the time.

06:54.515 --> 06:57.582
   I don't want your attention
   all of the time.

06:57.584 --> 07:00.152
    But maybe once, you could
    have made an exception,

07:00.154 --> 07:04.723
  done something I wanted to do
  that was important to me.

07:04.725 --> 07:06.691
 I missed most of my childhood,

07:06.693 --> 07:08.493
      missed my graduation

07:08.495 --> 07:10.762
      so I could be
      where you wanted me,

07:10.764 --> 07:13.064
    when you wanted me there.

07:13.066 --> 07:14.833
    I've fit into your life,

07:14.835 --> 07:18.136
   and now I'm doing something
   on my own terms.

07:18.138 --> 07:20.672
       Sweetie, I know
