07:34.087 --> 07:35.654
     Even when your daughter
     is plastered on

07:35.656 --> 07:36.888
   every magazine in New York,

07:36.890 --> 07:40.225
       it's like you
       still can't see me.

07:40.227 --> 07:42.027
      Cora, you can't just
      always run away.

07:42.029 --> 07:44.830
     I am not running away.

07:44.832 --> 07:48.767
    I am running towards
    something else, anything,

07:48.769 --> 07:50.168
 as long as it's not your idea.

07:50.170 --> 07:55.674
