 You know, the ocean, sunshine,
 "Welcome to Australia."

18:14.627 --> 18:18.563
   You're gonna give a girl
   from New York a dead fish?

18:18.565 --> 18:20.832
    Well, now it seems weird.

18:30.143 --> 18:33.678
        Oh! You're purdy.

