       Eye on the coconut.

24:36.876 --> 24:38.909
   It'll make you feel better.
   I promise.

24:38.911 --> 24:41.946
 Aim to hit it from underneath.
 -Better about what?

24:41.948 --> 24:44.782
 Better about whatever you need
 to feel better about.

24:44.784 --> 24:46.650
    Now, go low!
    She's gonna lollipop it!

24:48.554 --> 24:50.521
             -Go!
             -Whoo!

24:50.523 --> 24:53.224
            Come on!

24:53.226 --> 24:54.525
            You run

