        You run from me

24:57.630 --> 24:59.063
            Whoo-hoo!

25:04.537 --> 25:07.905
        You run from me

25:07.907 --> 25:09.707
            You run

25:09.709 --> 25:10.741
             You run

25:10.743 --> 25:12.676
        You run from me

25:12.678 --> 25:16.280
         You run from me

25:16.282 --> 25:17.681
            You run

25:17.683 --> 25:18.782
             You run

25:18.784 --> 25:21.085
        You run from me

25:36.702 --> 25:45.042
           'Cause I

