  -Wow. That sounds dangerous.
  -It's strange.

32:14.700 --> 32:18.368
   It's kind of like having
   my teen sister back again.

32:18.370 --> 32:20.037
        How's your, uh --
        How's your work?

32:20.039 --> 32:21.438
    Uh, busy. How about you?

32:21.440 --> 32:25.042
       Yeah, yeah, tied up
       with things here.

32:25.044 --> 32:27.978
  So, have you sold Blue Soul?

32:27.980 --> 32:29.246
      Why would I do that?

32:29.248 --> 32:30.614
I thought
 it wasn't going so well.

32:30.616 --> 32:33.383
      You don't know how
      it's going, actually.

32:33.385 --> 32:34.551
       It's just basic
       business principle.

32:34.553 --> 32:35.953
 It doesn't have to be personal.

32:35.955 --> 32:37.554
    Of course it's personal.

32:39.558 --> 32:42.059
   Isn't that why you deigned
   to visit us last time?

32:42.061 --> 32:43.527
      Because you were
      struggling with work,

32:43.529 --> 32:45.729
and you needed a break?
Because sometimes it's personal.

32:45.731 --> 32:47.364
I'm sorry to cut this short,

32:47.366 --> 32:51.401
     but I'm being hassled
     by my next appointment.

32:51.403 --> 32:53.603
     I just wanted to see
     if Cora was all right.

32:53.605 --> 32:57.307
I'm glad she's okay and that
you're both having fun together.

32:57.309 --> 32:58.976
     I'll talk to you later.

32:58.978 --> 33:02.012
         Okay. Sof, I...

33:04.083 --> 33:05.515
              Sof?

33:11.623 --> 33:14.291
    Cora. You're doing well.

